data.description: If you're looking for a home with plenty of space, this is the one! Renovated 6-bedroom/ 3 bath home in desirable River Ridge location. This home features a newly completed 1,000 square foot addition with high ceilings, 2-car garage, brand new A/C, and more! Primary suite has a large balcony, bay window sitting area, and spacious walk-in closet. Completely renovated kitchen and bathrooms. Situated on a beautiful corner lot just steps from Paradise Manor Community Club and Little Farms Playground. Vehicle access for boat/ RV parking. Don't miss this incredible home!
